{"id":607122,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/南京老周-控告你，为了法律的尊严！/","date":"2019-03-08T18:42:28Z","modified":"2019-03-08T18:46:48Z","title":"南京老周 | 控告你，为了法律的尊严！","content":"<p>作者：老周    来源：南京老周</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607124\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/1-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/1-11.jpg 504w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/1-11-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607125\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2-3.png 504w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2-3-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>今天，我来到这里，控告一个素不相识的人。<br />\n镇江市京口区检察院的彭莉检察官，是马捷被控挪用资金一案审查批捕的承办检察官，本周一（3月4日），该院案管中心告诉我3月3日已经受理江苏省公安厅直属公安局提请逮捕的案件，承办人为彭检察官。<span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br />\n从周一到今天，我无论是电话还是到检察院来，都找不到彭检察官，向案管、控申部门提交的法律文书，据说都已经转交彭检察官了，他们也都转达了听取辩护人意见的要求，然而……<br />\n对公安机关违法适用指定居所监视居住的监督，规定的办理期限只有七天，但距今将近七个月，仍然没有说法。<br />\n当事人认为公安机关不应当立案而立案，向检察院提出，检察机关即应启动监督程序。<br />\n检察院受理审查批捕期限总计为七天，今天已经是第六天，承办检察官拒接辩护人电话，拒绝听取律师意见，拒绝告知犯罪嫌疑人所涉犯罪事实，实质上剥夺了犯罪嫌疑人获得辩护的权利。<br />\n沟通无效，唯有控告！<br />\n我和你无冤无仇！<br />\n控告你，为了当事人的合法利益！<br />\n控告你，为了法律的尊严！<br />\n控告你，为了公平正义！<br />\n我在这里，等待检察长上班。</span></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607126\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/3-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/3-3.png 504w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/3-3-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607127\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/4-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/4-1.png 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/4-1-212x300.png 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607128\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/5-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/5-6.jpg 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/5-6-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607129\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/6-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/6-1.png 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/6-1-212x300.png 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607130\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-4.jpg 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/7-4-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607131\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8.png 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/8-212x300.png 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607132\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-1.jpg 551w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/9-1-212x300.jpg 212w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607133\" src=\"https://chinadi